        "name": "Sour Bomb",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You can mix ingredients with a powerful sour smell into an alchemical bomb to make its explosion an overpowering stench. Any creature hit by the bomb must attempt a Fortitude save against your class DC in addition to the bomb\u2019s normal effects.",
        "level": 10,
